en.title: FusionExcel Sponsors Miss Tourism International 2008 World Finals!
en.content: FusionExcel sponsored Miss Tourism International 2008 World Finals at Sunway Resort Hotel & Spa Grand Ballroom on 31st December 2008. There were 43 beauty queens from around the world vying for the title, which was won by Miss India. FusionExcel sponsored a subtitle "Miss FusionExcel Youthful" won by Miss Indonesia. It was a grand and colorful evening with the guests staying on for the final countdown to usher in New Year 2009. A party followed this for the VIP guests and the beauty queens. Amongst the VIPs were former Minister of Tourism Datuk Abdul Kadir Sheikh Fadzir, TV personality Dato Mahadzir Lokman, Sara Loo, Dato Jalaludin Hassan and Dato Paduka Toh Puan Seri Diraja Noor Aini Abdullah.
